This Tutorial Makes the NPC have the left click option to open up their shop.

So Go to your client side

Open up class5.java

Add this int [code]public static int NPCSTRADE[] = {};[/code] In the {} put the NPC IDS that you want to have the left-click trade. e.x {549, 546}

[code]Now search class5.method165(true, aClass30_Sub2_Sub2_60);[/code]

Under That add this

[code]for(int t : NPCSTRADE)

if(i == t) { 
		    class5.aStringArray66 = new String[5];
		    class5.aStringArray66[2] = "Trade";
		}[/code]

